🔹 1. Core Features

Here are the typical features a hotel booking website should have:

Guest Features

🏨 Browse hotels & rooms (search by location, date, price, amenities).

📅 Check availability of rooms.

🛏️ View room details (photos, price, amenities, reviews).

📝 Register & login (user account).

❤️ Save favorites (wishlist).

💳 Book rooms & make payments.

⭐ Add reviews after checkout.

📖 View booking history.

Host/Admin Features

👨‍💼 Host registration & verification.

🏠 Add/manage properties (hotels, apartments).

🚪 Add/manage rooms (availability, pricing, photos).

📊 Dashboard with stats (bookings, revenue).

🔄 Approve/Reject bookings.

🧾 Manage payments & refunds.

📝 Manage reviews.

Super Admin

👑 Manage all users & hosts.

🚫 Block/unblock accounts.

📊 Full site analytics.





        <!-- Gallery -->
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Gallery</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
          <% hotel.gallery.forEach(img => { %>
            <img src="<%= img %>" class="rounded-lg w-full h-40 object-cover" alt="Gallery image">
          <% }) %>
        </div> 

        <!-- Rooms -->
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Available Rooms</h3>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <% rooms.forEach(room => { %>
            <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
              <div class="mb-3 md:mb-0">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800"><%= room.type %></h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm"><%= room.amenities.join(", ") %></p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-center md:text-right">
                <p class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">$<%= room.price_per_night %> / night</p>
                <a href="/hotels/<%= hotel.id %>/booking/<%= room.id %>" 
                   class="mt-2 inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
                  Book Now
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Quick Info -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Hotel Info</h3>
        <p><span class="font-semibold">📍 Location:</span> <%= hotel.address %></p>
        <p><span class="font-semibold">⭐ Rating:</span> <%= hotel.rating %>/5</p>
        <p><span class="font-semibold">🕒 Check-in:</span> 2:00 PM</p>
        <p><span class="font-semibold">🕒 Check-out:</span> 12:00 PM</p>
      </div>
